snippet.title: Rocket Arena - Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Rocket Arena is an explosive 3v3 all-rockets shooter where you’re never out of the action. Prepare to launch into the fray July 14! http://x.ea.com/63474

Welcome to a world where the rules are written in rocket fuel.

Rockets rule everything in Rocket Arena. Master your hero’s unique rockets and abilities to dominate the arena and become a champion! Try out an ever-growing roster of diverse heroes with distinctive powers. Unearth new strategies and tactics based on your squad, explore a wide variety of dynamic maps, and discover the true depth of rocket gameplay.

Ready to be blown away?

Pre-order now on Xbox One, Origin and Steam for PC: http://x.ea.com/63475. Rocket Arena will also be available on the PlayStation®4.

Music: 
Fire, Ready, Aim
Performed by Green Day


#Rocket Arena #LetsRocket #WelcomeToCrater
